    This package contains controllers for charts of amcharts
    es.uvigo.esei.amchartsJava.core.controllers.graphs
    This package contains controllers for graphs of amcharts, in amcharts only exists AmGraph.
    es.uvigo.esei.amchartsJava.core.controllers.trendLines

    es.uvigo.esei.amchartsJava.core.model
    This package contains basic objects used in app, all classes extends IModel class.
    es.uvigo.esei.amchartsJava.core.model.charts
    This package contains charts used by app
    es.uvigo.esei.amchartsJava.core.validators
    This package contains validators to paths, idiom and values of properties,also cast to concrete chart,graph,guide,trendLine or Axis
